name: "StarStruck [The Mixes]" CD - Soneni
description: Described as "a sublime piece of soulful house", by BBC Radio 1 DJ Ras Kwame, Soneni's debut single "StarStruck" (produced by Funk For The Soul)is now available in CD format and includes: StarStruck [Original - Radio Edit], StarStruck [Live Band Version], Fly So High [Bonus Track] and StarStruck [Original - Extended Club Mix].
